"Indeed," a smirk upon her face. "Then I welcome you, fellow Decepticons." 

She glanced at the craft. "Is the ship salvagable? IF not, leave it. Take 
with you that of major importance." 

"We shall mark this area with beacon & defense stakes. I don't want the 
Autobots & Maximals in this area." As she pulled out a foot long bolt from a 
compartment in her thigh, then jabbed it into the ground near the fallen ship.
